<L>__{exterior hotel bellavista, pov from balcony day}
<A>__{hotel staff swarm around the vehicles which discharge a procession of religious, including an ancient cardinal in scarlet robes and the cardinal's secretary. priests follow as the cardinal heads inside the hotel. guido is intrigued, hurries out of his hotel room.}
